<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px; background-color: #f5f5f5;">
        <h2>Your OTP for Registration</h2>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with us. Here is your One-Time Password (OTP):</p>
        <h3 style="font-size: 24px; color: #007bff;"> 
            <%= otp %> <!-- This will be replaced with the actual OTP value from the server -->
        </h3>
        <p>Please use this OTP to complete your registration.</p>
        <p>Regards, <br> The Team Spitty</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
